headline: Looking At The Narrative For CME Group (CME) As Analyst Views Shift
summary: CME Group’s fair value estimate has been nudged higher to roughly US$296.71 per share, with the discount rate trimmed to around 7.90% and revenue growth assumptions lifted to about 5.44%. This reflects a fresh round of recalibration from the analyst community. These tweaks sit against a backdrop where several bullish research shops have raised their price targets and one major bank has adjusted its view in both directions, highlighting both interest in the story and some ongoing debate around...
